{"tid":1698007,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新地沒有答問環節 小股東：佢梗係向住阿爺","createTime":"2019-11-07T08:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:24:05.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd995f3b311c0cb525bc675e5afc8ef8a413a16e","tid":1698007,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191107/large/1573104753_7f18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573104753_7f18.jpg&h=b00c936d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新地（016）今日召開股東大會，其中一項為重選華潤置地（1109）前主席兼共產黨員吳向東先生為董事。主席郭炳聯在宣讀各項動議後，迅即離場，懷疑迴避回答政治問題。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在場小股東還未來得及舉手發問，郭炳聯已拉隊離場，故沒有股東問答環節，整場股東會僅召開15分鐘便草草結束，令在場小股東感到愕然及不滿。小股東黃先生十分勞氣表示，「自己只係小股東，講嚟都嘥氣，佢梗係向住阿爺，我哋邊可以表達到意見。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另一位小股東江先生表示，整場股東會，讀動議用了十多分鐘，他們就離場了，完全沒有時間給股東表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n新地發言人聯絡本報回應指，答問環節並非突然取消，又指現場並沒有股東發問問題，過往亦試過沒有股東發問而沒有答問環節。不過發言人所指「現場並沒有股東發問問題」，與現實情況不符。<br />\n記者：吳美茸 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191107/60240409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F60240409&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK1c%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=7658d26a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F60240409&h=33ee3aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191107/60240409</a>"},{"pid":"4fc2a85d4e85a748d7bb56f432a155ac323d7ba2","tid":1698007,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"一早有黨委"}]}